didn't get in till 3 and had an early start which meant death to me ! i am back in ku bar with dartz! again tonight which means another late night so a long day at uni then work then ku bar..i probo will not be alive tomoz ! i think i need to stop burning the candle at both ends ! hahah wayy

On the plus side ! should so how good me hair looks today ! havn't washed it for three days ! and its sweaty as ha ! mint !
